  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether treatment with a new drug called
      ZK-Epothilone (ZK-Epo) in patients with metastatic breast cancer helps to decrease or stop
      tumor growth.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study has previously been registered by Berlex, Inc. Berlex, Inc. has been renamed to
      Bayer HealthCare Pharmaceuticals, Inc.Bayer HealthCare Pharmaceuticals, Inc.is the sponsor of
      this study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
